high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the wine bottle from the lower cabinet.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the wine bottle in the fridge, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter to the right of the bread.
Put the wine bottle on the counter near the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place chilled wine onto the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter, take a left and go to the cabinet.
Open the rightmost cabinet and remove the bottle of wine.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the bottle of wine in the fridge to get cold, then remove the bottle of wine from the fridge.
Turn around and go to the counter where the bread is.
Put the cold bottle of wine on the counter in front of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bottle of wine on the counter.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the stove
pick up a bottle from the cabinet
move to the fridge behind you
chill the bottle for a moment in the fridge
move to the counter behind you with the bread
put the bottle on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wine bottle near a loaf of bread.
